#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There is three main steps to create a new skin: creating the folders "
#| "hierarchy; creating the graphics, all pooled inside a SVG file; and then "
#| "placing sprites and naming things using &kappname;."
msgid ""
"There is three main steps to create a new skin: creating the folders "
"hierarchy; creating the graphics, all pooled inside a &SVG; file; and then "
"placing sprites and naming things using &i18n-ksirkskineditor;."
msgstr ""
"Postoje tri glavna koraka za stvaranje nove teme: stvaranje folder "
"hijerarhije; stvaranje grafike, sve udruženo unutar SVG datoteke; a zatim "
"stavljanje sprajtova i imenovanje stvari koristeći &kappname;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a &ksirk; skin"
msgstr "Kreiranje &ksirk; koža"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&ksirk; is fully skinable. For who have graphic capabilities, creating a "
#| "new skin is as simple as copying an existing one, editing or changing the "
#| "graphics and updating the data in a .desktop configuration file, which is "
#| "done using the &kappname;. A last step is to edit the file describing "
#| "what to install."
msgid ""
"&ksirk; is fully skinable. For who have graphic capabilities, creating a new "
"skin is as simple as copying an existing one, editing or changing the "
"graphics and updating the data in a <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</"
"literal> configuration file, which is done using the &i18n-ksirkskineditor;. "
"A last step is to edit the file describing what to install."
msgstr ""
"&ksirk; je u potpunosti zaštićen. Za one koji imaju grafičke mogućnosti, "
"stvaranje nove teme je jednostavno kao kopiranje već postojeće, uređivanje "
"ili promjena grafike i ažuriranje podataka u a .desktop configuration file, "
"koja se obavlja pomoću &kappname;. A posljednji korak je da uredite datoteku "
"opisujući šta instalirati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "All examples (text and images) are taken from the default skin of &ksirk;"
msgid ""
"All examples (text and images) are taken from the default skin of &ksirk;."
msgstr ""
"Svi primjeri (tekst i slike) su uzeti iz podrazumijevane teme ili &ksirk;"

